-dasha-zhukova-mother-with-roman-abramovich-ties%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20elite%20British%20society%20magazine%20Tatler%20describes%3C%2Fa%3E%20Zhukova%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20sprawling%20web%20of%20power%20that%20encompasses%20the%20art%20world%2C%20Russian%20oligarchs%20and%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20shipping%20dynasties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20has%20Jewish-Russian%20heritage%2C%20and%20was%20previously%20married%20to%20Russian%20oil%20billionaire%20and%20financier%20Alexander%20Zhukhov.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FnpsoN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Yorker%20in%202010%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20described%20her%20family%20as%20being%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMoscow%20intelligentsia%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20she%20met%20her%20first%20husband%20when%20the%20two%20were%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20Dasha%20Zhukhova.%20They%20divorced%20when%20she%20was%20three%2C%20and%20Alexander%20went%20on%20to%20make%20a%20fortune%20in%20oil%20and%20finance%20when%20Soviet%20authorities%20began%20to%20loosen%20restrictions%20on%20private%20enterprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fa71190e8-2934-11e2-9591-00144feabdc0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPer%20the%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zhukova%20left%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%201990%2C%20when%20she%20was%20in%20her%20thirties.%20She%20took%20a%20position%20at%20the%20Baylor%20College%20of%20Medicine%20in%20Houston%20in%201990%2C%20Zhukhova%2C%20and%20moved%20there%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20then%20nine%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20was%20first%20thought%20to%20be%20temporary%2C%20her%20daughter%20told%20the%20FT%2C%20but%20they%20lived%20there%20for%20years%20until%20Zhukova%20was%20offered%20an%20opportunity%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20study%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20she%20retired%2C%20Zhukova%20was%20a%20professor%20of%20biology%20with%20several%20peer-reviewed%20scientific%20articles%20to%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20daughter%20described%20her%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%20scientist%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20interested%20in%20substance%20than%20aesthetics.%26quot%3B%20She%20recalled%20a%20childhood%20filled%20with%20%26quot%3Bgeeky%26quot%3B%20graduate%20students%20visiting%20the%20house%2C%20the%20FT%20reported%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElena%20also%20has%20twins%2C%20a%20boy%20and%20a%20girl%2C%20from%20another%20relationship%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fartanddesign%2F2009%2Foct%2F04%2Fdasha-zhukova-interview-roman-abramovich%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20Guardian%20profile%20of%20Dasha%20Zhukhova.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20Zhukova%20is%20an%20art%20collector%2C%20socialite%2C%20and%20businesswoman%2C%20who%20was%20married%20to%20Roman%20Abramovich%2C%20a%20Russian%20oligarch%20and%20the%20former%20owner%20of%20Chelsea%20FC.%20The%20couple%20had%20two%20children%20before%20their%20divorce%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2Froman-abramovich-transfers-92m-of-property-to-ex%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Post%20citing%20property%20records%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3EAbramovich%20transferred%20ownership%20of%20%2492%20million%20of%20New%20York%20City%20property%20to%20Dasha%20Zhukova%20after%20their%20divorce%2C%20including%20a%205-storey%20Upper%20East%20Side%20mansion%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDasha%20Zhukova%20is%20currently%20married%20to%20Stavros%20Niarchos%20II%2C%20grandson%20of%20Greek%20shipping%20magnate%20Stavros%20Niarchos.%20The%20c