elopment%20and%20sensitivities%20involved%20for%20its%20micro-%2C%20small-%20and%20medium-sized%20firms%2C%20the%20officials%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20a%20trade%20accord%20is%20critical%20for%20India's%20ambition%20to%20become%20a%20manufacturing%20powerhouse%2C%20while%20the%20UK%20is%20seeking%20to%20clinch%20new%20deals%20to%20highlight%20the%20benefits%20of%20Brexit.%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20PM%20Modi%20will%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter%20face-to-face%20at%20a%20Group%20of%2020%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Trade%20Ministry%20didn't%20respond%20to%20an%20e-mailed%20request%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20UK%20trade%20department%20said%20its%20made%20%26quot%3Bgood%20progress%26quot%3B%20in%20closing%20chapters%20and%20both%20countries%20are%20now%20%26quot%3Blaser-focused%26quot%3B%20on%20goods%2C%20services%20and%20investment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20cannot%20comment%20on%20ongoing%20negotiations%2C%20we%20are%20clear%20that%20we%20will%20only%20sign%20when%20we%20have%20a%20deal%20that%20is%20fair%2C%20balanced%2C%20and%20ultimately%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20British%20people%20and%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20negotiations%20on%20visas%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20particularly%20sensitive.%20India%20has%20long%20demanded%20increased%20access%20for%20its%20citizens%2C%20but%20the%20UK's%20vote%20for%20Brexit%20in%202016%20was%20fueled%20in%20part%20by%20calls%20for%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20numbers%20of%20people%20coming%20into%20the%20country%2C%20and%20immigration%20remains%20a%20hot-button%20topic%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20difficulties%20Sunak's%20government%20faces%2C%20net%20migration%20to%20the%20UK%20reached%20a%20record%20606%2C000%20people%20last%20year%2C%20while%20separate%20visa%20data%20has%20shown%20one%20in%20three%20residence%20visas%20were%20granted%20to%20Indian%20workers.%20A%20UK%20official%20said%20talks%20are%20centering%20on%20time-limited%20business%20visas%20for%20highly%20skilled%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%2C%20if%20it%20materializes%2C%20will%20be%20India's%20biggest%20and%20most%20ambitious%20free%20trade%20agreement%20to%20date.%20This%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20many%20western%20economies%20are%20pinning%20their%20hopes%20on%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20to%20become%20a%20bulwark%20against%20China's%20growing%20economic%20and%20military%20clout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGood%20Progress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20two%20nations%20have%20been%20reluctant%20to%20set%20a%20date%20for%20completing%20the%20talks%20after%20missing%20a%20deadline%20last%20year%2C%20negotiations%20have%20been%20progressing%20well%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20Indian%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20decision%20to%20visit%20Britain%20last%20month%20put%20political%20momentum%20behind%20talks%2C%20one%20UK%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunak%20administration%20is%20also%20considering%20signing%20an%20agreement%20that%20will%20help%20Indians%20claw%20back%20half%20a%20billion%20pounds%20in%20payments%20made%20by%20them%20toward%20Britain's%20social%20security%20system%2C%20the%20Indian%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20looking%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20import%20duty%20on%20cars%20to%2075%25%20from%20the%20current%20100%25.%20However%2C%20this%20will%20exclude%20small%20capacity%20cars%20and%20there%20would%20be%20a%20cap%20on%20the%20number%20of%20vehicles%20sold%20under%20these%20lower%20tariffs%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20on%20scotch%20whisky%2C%20New%20Delhi%20may%20slash%20duties%20to%20100%25%20from%20the%20existing%20150%25%20charged%20above%20a%20minimum%20import%20price.%20The%20premium%20categ