y%20announced%20first%20lists%20of%20candidates%20for%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20due%20later%20this%20year.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20BJP%20has%20announced%20names%20of%20candidates%20even%20before%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20announces%20the%20poll%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20announced%2021%20candidates%20for%20the%2090-member%20Chhattisgarh%20Assembly%20and%2039%20for%20the%20230-member%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20BJP's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-amit-shah-jp-nadda-bjp-bjps-advance-prep-on-5-year-end-state-polls-pm-to-chair-key-meet-today-4301381%5C%22%3Ecentral%20election%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20party's%20decision-making%20body%20for%20selection%20of%20candidates%20and%20preparation%20of%20poll%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leadership's%20unprecedented%20decision%20to%20announce%20candidates'%20names%20well%20in%20advance%20appears%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20identifying%20friction%20within%20the%20ranks%20so%20that%20issues%20can%20be%20resolved%20well%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20poll%20setback%20in%20Karnataka%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20party%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20for%20another%20debacle.%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20among%20five%20states%20going%20to%20polls%20later%20this%20year%2C%20along%20with%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20these%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Telangana%20are%20ruled%20by%20Opposition%20forces.%20In%20Mizoram%2C%20BJP's%20ties%20with%20ally%20and%20ruling%20party%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20are%20strained%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Manipur%20unrest.%20And%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20neck-to-neck%20fight%20is%20expected%20be