ndia-news%2Fbjp-names-chhattisgarh-madhya-pradesh-candidates-a-first-before-poll-dates-4305459%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20More%20than%20100%20arrested%20after%20churches%20burned%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692270965000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F134CC%2Fproduction%2F_130825097_gettyimages-1604182351.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66517901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20gatherings%20in%20the%20area%20are%20also%20banned%20for%20seven%20days%20after%20violence%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Jaranwala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66517901%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66517901.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66517901.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Trump's%20Legal%20Mess%20And%20American%20Democracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20surreal%20times%20in%20the%20US.%20Even%20as%20the%20political%20system%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20next%20year's%20Presidential%20elections%2C%20the%20legal%20drama%20being%20played%20out%20in%20various%20courtrooms%20is%20shaping%20the%20political%20dynamic%20more%20potently%20than%20political%20debates.%20In%20fact%2C%20politics%20has%20been%20subsumed%20by%20the%20legal%20issues%20surrounding%20key%20political%20actors%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20He%20will%20be%20turning%20himself%20in%20to%20police%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Georgia%2C%20where%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20booked%20at%20the%20Fulton%20County%20Jail%20in%20Atlanta%20before%20being%20arraigned%20at%20the%20courthouse.%20Along%20with%2018%20others%2C%20Trump%20was%20indicted%20earlier%20this%20week%20for%20alleged%20attempts%20to%20overturn%20his%202020%20election%20loss%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20only%20the%20latest%20one%2C%20Trump%20has%20been%20criminally%20indicted%20in%20three%20other%20cases%2C%20including%20in%20a%20federal%20investigation%20into%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20the%20result%20of%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%2C%20his%20alleged%20mishandling%20of%20classified%20material%20after%20he%20left%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20paying%20hush-money%20to%20the%20adult%20film%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels%20before%20the%202016%20election.%20In%20any%20other%20time%20and%20for%20any%20other%20politician%2C%20any%20of%20this%20would%20have%20been%20the%20end%20of%20the%20political%20road.%20But%20such%20are%20vagaries%20of%20American%20politics%20today%20that%20Trump%20seems%20to%20using%20these%20as%20badges%20of%20honour.%20In%20his%20usual%20acerbic%20style%2C%20Trump%20has%20decided%20to%20hold%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20news%20conference%26quot%3B%20next%20week%20to%20present%20an%20%26quot%3Birrefutable%20report%26quot%3B%20on%20voter%20fraud%20from%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20not%20the%20only%20drama%20in%20town.%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20son%2C%20Hunter%20Biden's%20shenanigans%20in%20the%20courtroom%20have%20not%20been%20any%20less%20riveting.%20He%20has%20been%20under%20federal%20investigation%20since%202019%20and%20recently%2C%20after%20a%20plea%20deal%20on%20tax%20and%20gun%20charges%20against%20him%20collapsed%2C%20a%20special%20counsel%20was%20appointed%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20to%20look%20into%20his%20case%2C%20with%20a%20jury%20trial%20looking%20imminent.%20Where%20President%20Biden%20has%20predictably%20stood%20by%20his%20son%2C%20the%20Republicans%20have%20gone%20after%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20focusing%20on%20his%20business%20interests%20in%20China%20and%20Ukraine.%20In%20fact%2C%20only%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20then%20President%20Trump%20had%20pressured%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20to%20investigate%20Hunter's%20dealings%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20natural%20gas%20company%2C%20Burisma%20Holdings%20(where%20Hunter%20served%20on%20the%20board)%20did%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20Trump's%20first%20impeachment%20start%20in%202019%20for%20soliciting%20foreign%20interference%20in%20the%202020%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20sleaze%2C%20corruption%20and%20political%20brinkmanship%20evident%20in%20these%20episodes%20is%20usually%20associated%20with%20Third%20world%20countries%20with%20weak%20institutions%20and%20personalized%20politics.%20Washington%20is%20usually%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20advising%20such%20nations%20on%20how%20to%20conduct%20their%20domestic%20affairs.%20But%20today%20the%20shoe%20is%20in%20the%20other%20foot.%20The%20US%20looks%20like%20a%20pale%20replica%20of%20its%20glorious%20past%20as%20a%20democracy.%20It%20is%20unable%20to%20set%20its%20own%20house%20in%20order%20and%20its%20credibility%20across%20the%20world%20is%20being%20challenged%20with%20autocracies%20like%20China%20and%20Russia%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20case%20for%20the%20superiority%20of%20their%20own%20models%20of%20political%20governance.%20It%20is%20laughable%2C%20but%20that's%20what%20it%20has%20come%20down%20to%20in%20the%20age%20of%20Trump%20and%20Hunter%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20continues%20to%20see%20his%20support%20rise%20among%20grassroots%20Republicans.%20The%20more%20indictments%20he%20receives%2C%20the%20stronger%20the%20resolve%20of%20his%20supporters%20to%20send%20him%20back%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20There%20is%20an%20alternative%20reality%20that%20shapes%20the%20worldview%20of%20Trump%20supporters%20where%20their%20own%20nation's%20institutions%20are%20seen%20are%20corrupt%20and%20partial.%20Personalities%20tower%20over%20institutions%2C%20something%20that%20America's%20founding%20fathers%20tried%20so%20hard%20to%20avoid%20in%20the%20way%20they%20framed%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20nomination%20process%20has%20already%20begun%20and%20monthly%20debates%20among%20the%20party's%20nominees%20are%20starting%20next%20week.%20Trump%20remains%20far%20ahead%20of%20everyone%20else%20with%20his%20campaign%20donations%20overflowing%20and%20his%20supporters%20being%20the%20loudest.%20As%20his%20trials%20begin%20later%20this%20year%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20manage%20his%20court%20appearances%20with%20his%20campaign%20for%20the%20Republican%20nomination.%20Trump's%20supporters%20believe%20in%20his%20assessment%20that%20the%20legal%20cases%20against%20him%20are%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20him%20from%20another%20White%20House%20run.%20Their%20strong%20conviction%20in%20this%20argument%20is%20reflective%20of%20how%20deep%20goes%20the%20social%20and%20political%20polarization%20in%20the%20US.%20So%20deep%20that%20huge%20constituencies%20are%20willing%20to%20bet%20on%20the%20worst%20intentions%20of%20others.%20Due%20to%20the%20support%20for%20Trump%20in%20the%20Republican%20primaries%2C%20instead%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20ex-President%2C%20his%20Republican%20opponents%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20criticize%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20the%20American%20legal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20breakdown%20of%20the%20social%20order%20in%20the%20US%20is%20now%20firmly%20embedded%20in%20its%20politics.%20Trump%20is%20just%20one%20manifestation%20of%20that%20reality.%20His%20campaign%20may%20or%20may%20not%20succeed%20but%20the%20challenges%20for%20American%20democracy%20will%20continue.%20For%20many%20of%20his%20supporters%2C%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20they%20continue%20to%20support%20Trump%20politically%2C%20knowing%20well%20that%20Biden%20had%20defeated%20him%20last%20time%20in%20swing%20states.%20The%20primary%20campaign%20is%20different%20from%20the%20national%20one%20and%20most%20Republican%20voters%20will%20have%20to%20take%20it%20into%20account%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20knows%20how%20to%20play%20to%20the%20gallery.%20Courtrooms%20will%20be%20his%20stage.%20The%20more%20media%20time%20he%20gets%2C%20the%20better%20it%20is%20for%20him%20to%20rally%20his%20base.%20His%20Republican%20opponents%20remain%20unimpressive%20so%20far%2C%20failing%20to%20make%20a%20mark.%20%C2%A0Trump's%20actions%2C%20in%20the%20court%20and%20outside%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20dominate%20the%20election%20cycle%2C%20helping%20him%20in%20easily%20entering%20the%20Presidential%20contest.%20What%20this%20does%20to%20American%20democracy%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20another%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692270840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Ff3ni69lo_donald-trump-afp_625x300_05_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-legal-mess-and-american-democracy-4305700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20strange%20times%20in%20the%20US.%20Even%20as%20the%20political%20system%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20next%20year's%20Presidential%20elections%2C%20the%20legal%20drama%20being%20played%20out%20in%20various%20courtrooms%20is%20shaping%20the%20political%20dynamic%20more%20potently%20than%20political%20debates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-legal-mess-and-american-democracy-4305700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-legal-mess-and-ame