p%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20asked%20for%20the%20farmers'%20help%20finance%20efforts%20to%20make%20sure%20Trump%20was%20elected%20to%20a%20second%20term.%20But%20Giuliani%20wasn't%20seeking%20a%20donation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0he%20wanted%20them%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20was%20filed%20this%20month%20by%20a%20Munger-owned%20LLC%2C%20one%20of%20several%20entities%20controlled%20by%20the%20multinational%20agro-barons%2C%20who%20also%20hold%20part%20ownership%20of%20Naturipe%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20producer%20of%20blueberries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20was%20working%20with%20Yale%20and%20cannabis%20investor%20George%20Dickson%20III%2C%20per%20the%20suit.%20The%20lawsuit%20claims%20that%20the%20three%20men%20pitched%20the%20farmers%20on%20a%20film%20that%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20possible%20'kill%20shot'%20to%20Biden's%20presidential%20campaign.%26quot%3B%20The%20three%20men%20%26quot%3Ball%20represented%20that%20they%20possessed%20key%20documents%20that%20were%20'smoking%20guns'%20that%20would%20establish%20that%20the%20Ukrainian%20government%20engaged%20in%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20exchange%20with%20the%20Biden%20family%20to%20benefit%20Burisma%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurisma%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20the%20energy%20company%20that%20paid%20Hunter%20Biden%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20sit%20on%20its%20board.%20Republicans%20have%20long%20alleged%20but%20have%20never%20proven%20a%20nexus%20between%20Hunter's%20work%20on%20Burisma's%20board%20and%20Joe%20Biden's%20efforts%2C%20as%20vice%20president%2C%20to%20remove%20a%20Ukrainian%20prosecutor%20who%20was%20investigating%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllegedly%2C%20the%20film%20was%20supposed%20to%20reveal%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmoking%20gun%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20take%20the%20Bidens%20down%2C%20secure%20Trump's%20second%20term%2C%20and%20enrich%20the%20Mungers%20in%20the%20process.%20%26quot%3BYale%20and%20Dickson%20represented%20that%20this%20documentary%20movie%20was%20going%20to%20be%20bigger%20and%20more%20profitable%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmichael-moore-new-documentary-fahrenheit-11-9-looks-at-trump-obama-clinton-flint-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20Moore's%20'Fahrenheit%209%2F11%2C'%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20earned%20%24200%20million%20at%20the%20box%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mungers%2C%20who%20had%20given%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20Republican%20candidates%2C%20were%20sold.%20They%20turned%20over%20%241%20million%20to%20finance%20the%20film%2C%20according%20to%20promissory%20notes%20attached%20to%20the%20complaint%20as%20exhibits.%20Out%20of%20that%20money%2C%20%24300%2C000%20allegedly%20went%20to%20Giuliani%20himself%3B%20the%20rest%20%26quot%3Bwas%20stolen%20by%20Dickson%20and%20Yale%20for%20their%20own%20personal%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20promises%20allegedly%20made%20by%20the%20film's%20backers%20materialized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20was%20never%20made%20or%20released.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-biggest-successes-failures-second-year-recap-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20won%20the%202020%20election.%20And%20the%20Mungers'%20million-dollar%20bet%20vanished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%2C%20after%20conducting%20interviews%20with%20various%20Ukrainian%20officials%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20produce%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmoking%20gun.%26quot%3B%20As%20Election%20Day%20drew%20near%2C%20his%20attention%20drifted%20from%20filmmaking%20to%20a%20different%20October%20surprise%20%E2%80%94%20emails%20and%20other%20data%20obtained%20from%20Hunter%20Biden's%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20Giuliani's%20opposition%20research%20effort%2C%20Trump%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20second%20term.%20Giuliani's%20efforts%20to%20erase%20that%20democratic%20outcome%2C%20first%20with%20spurious%20lawsuits%20and%20then%20with%20denialism%20and%20a%20call%20to%20%26quot%3Btrial%20by%20combat%26quot%3B%20now%20have%20him%20facing%20criminal%20charges%20in%20Georgia.%20He%20also%20faces%20a%20civil%20suit%20filed%20by%20his%20former%20assistant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-noelle-dunphy-settlement-discussions-sexual-assault-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENoelle%20Dunphy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20accuses%20Giuliani%20of%20wage%20theft%20and%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20is%20not%20a%20defendant%20in%20the%20Mungers'%20California%20lawsuit%20over%20the%20film.%20But%20he%20and%20Dickson%20were%20reportedly%20investigated%20by%20the%20FBI%20over%20the%20movie.%20The%20bureau%20searched%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-investigates-rudy-giuliani-over-biden-ukraine-film-report-says-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDickson's%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20film%202021%2C%20but%20no%20charges%20were%20ever%20filed%20in%20connection%20with%20it.%20The%20suit%20also%20includes%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Doe%26quot%3B%20defendants%2C%20and%20could%20be%20updated%20to%20include%20more%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20about%20Yale%20and%20Dickson's%20efforts%20to%20raise%20%2410%20million%20to%20finance%20the%20film%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.motherjones.com%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F05%2Frudy-giuliani-is-looking-for-10-million-to-finance-a-ukraine-biden-film%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20by%20Mother%20Jones.%20The%20magazine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%