ot%20only%20leaves%20out%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20but%20also%20the%20state%20BJP%20president%20CP%20Joshi%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Rajendra%20Rathore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20other%20key%20leaders%20who%20are%20not%20on%20the%20committee%20are%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20former%20state%20BJP%20president%20Satish%20Poonia.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20party%20sources%20had%20hinted%20at%20these%20five%20stalwarts%20collectively%20leading%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20in%20less%20than%20three%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20announced%20that%20the%20state%20election%20management%20committee%20will%20have%2021%20members%20and%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20former%20MP%20Narayan%20Lal%20Panchariya.%20The%20panel%20tasked%20with%20preparing%20the%20election%20manifesto%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20Union%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20and%20have%2025%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20other%20big%20names%20included%20in%20the%20panels%20are%20MP%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Rajyavardhan%20Singh%20Rathore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20launched%20several%20campaigns%20to%20corner%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20especially%20on%20corruption%20and%20crime%20against%20women.%20While%20the%20party's%20Mahila%20Morcha%20has%20made%20increasing%20crime%20an%20election%20issue%2C%20the%20'Nahi%20Sahega%20Rajasthan'%20campaign%20is%20targeting%20the%20government%20on%20corruption%2C%20paper%20leak%20and%20farmer%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20is%20to%20find%20answers%20to%20the%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20including%20the%20Right%20to%20Health%20Bill%2C%20the%20Gig%20Workers'%20Bill%20and%20the%20power%20and%20gas%20subsidies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20success%20of%20the%20five%20guarantees%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20Congress'%20victory%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20is%20banking%20on%20these%20schemes%20to%20ensure%20it%20gets%20a%20second%20term%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692269340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj7am5oeo_vasundhara-raje_625x300_17_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-sets-up-2-panels-for-rajasthan-polls-leaves-out-state-chief-vasundhara-raje-4305560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20big%20announcement%20notable%20more%20for%20its%20omissions%20than%20inclusions%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20has%20set%20up%20two%20committees%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-sets-up-2-panels-for-rajasthan-polls-leaves-out-state-chief-vasundhara-raje-4305560%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-sets-up-2-panels-for-rajasthan-polls-leaves-out-state-chief-vasundhara-raje-4305560%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-sets-up-2-panels-for-rajasthan-polls-leaves-out-state-chief-vasundhara-raje-4305560%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%20100%20arrested%2C%20probe%20ordered%20in%20attacks%20on%20churches%20and%20homes%20of%20Christians%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692269208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102803649%2Cimgsize-141396.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fover-100-arrested-probe-ordered-in-attacks-on-churches-and-homes-of-christians-in-pakistan%2Farticleshow%2F102803293.cms%22%