ever%2C%20bond%20yields%20have%20risen%20above%204%25%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-tech-stocks-nasdaq-composite-inflation-cpi-ppi-2023-8%5C%22%3Eequity%20rally%20has%20petered%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20investors%20fretting%20that%20the%20Fed%20might%20hold%20interest%20rates%20at%20a%20higher%20level%20for%20longer%20as%20part%20of%20its%20effort%20to%20tame%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Treasury%20yields%20rise%2C%20they%20become%20more%20attractive%20to%20investors%20relative%20to%20stocks%20because%20they%20offer%20similar%20returns%20at%20a%20lower%20risk%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20should%20buy%20bonds%20in%20case%20a%20%26quot%3BGoldilocks%26quot%3B%20scenario%20%E2%80%93%20where%20both%20growth%20and%20inflation%20hover%20at%20a%20level%20that's%20%26quot%3Bjust%20right%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%93%20doesn't%20play%20out%2C%20Shalett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBetter-than-feared%20economic%20developments%20have%20apparently%20delivered%20an%20immaculate%20soft-landing%2C%20emboldening%20equity%20investors%20to%20price%20out%20the%20potential%20for%20further%20profits%20recession%20or%20an%20eventual%20economic%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20that%20optimistic%20scenario%20could%20yet%20play%20out%2C%20paying%20peak%20multiples%20on%20reaccelerating%20earnings%20and%20assuming%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20strike%20us%20as%20counting%20on%20a%20Goldilocks%20scenario%20despite%20unsure%20odds%2C%26quot%3B%20Shalett%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20investors%20should%20consider%20hedges%20for%20their%20high-priced%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-bond-yields-treasurys-inflation-investing-morgan-stanley-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692268613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd4912f5d4870019e2044b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fstock-market-crash-bond-yields-treasurys-inflation-investing-morgan-stanley-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bond%20yields%20have%20shot%20up%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20while%20the%20stock-market%20rally%20is%20showing%20signs%20of%20finally%20fizzling%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gglover%40insider.com%20(George%20Glover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fstock-market-crash-bond-yields-treasurys-inflation-investing-morgan-stanley-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Interface%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Jihad%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20False%20Indian%20Articulation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17160453%2Fc6e7db8f-74ee-43fd-8bc8-583eba8ef9ff.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaharashtra%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20declared%20on%20August%205%2C%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20intention%20of%20enacting%20a%20law%20against%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20to%20stop%20the%20luring%20of%20innocent%20Hindu%20girls%20by%20Muslims%20into%20wedlock%20and%20then%20converting%20them%20to%20Islam.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20phrase%20love%20jihad%20appeared%20first%20time%20as%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20in%202009%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatan%20Prabhat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Janajagruti%20Samiti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20was%20later%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad.%20It%20became%20a%20central%20agenda%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20governments%20in%20various%20states%20after%202014.%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20are%20among%20the%20prominent%20states%20that%20have%20such%20a%20law.%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20law%20mandates%20couples%20to%20declare%20religion%20and%20income.%20While%20occasional%20media%20reports%20bring%20out%20such%20marriages%20and%20the%20controversy%20they%20go%20through%2C%20there%20is%20no%20precise%20figure%20on%20the%20number%20of%20such%20cases.%20Hindu%20vigilante%20groups%20on%20prowl%20coupled%20with%20a%20biased%20and%20partisan%20police%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20arrests%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20%E2%80%98jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20Islamic%20concept%2C%20love%20jihad%20obviously%20securitizes%20marriage%20between%20a%20Muslim%20male%20and%20women%20of%20Hindu%20(primarily)%20and%20other%20religions%20as%20jihad.%20Apparently%2C%20the%20motive%20behind%20coining%20this%20term%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20patriarchal%20and%20majoritarian%20Hindutva%20project%2C%20is%20to%20declare%20jihad%20as%20an%20aggressive%20ongoing%20struggle%20for%20both%20superiority%20and%20conversion.%C2%A0%20Joined%20with%20%E2%80%98love%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20is%20being%20portrayed%20as%20a%20religio-cultural%20and%20demographic%20offensive%20against%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20look%20at%20the%20concept%20of%20jihad%20in%20the%20holy%20Quran%20does%20not%20convey%20force%2C%20offensive%2C%20aggression%20or%20violence.%20Since%20there%20are%20approximately%2041%20verses%20out%20of%20total%206%2C236%20that%20mention%20jihad%20and%20its%20derivatives%20in%20the%20holy%20book%2C%20its%20multiple%20uses%2C%20implications%20and%20polysemy%20are%20apparent.%20There%20are%20also%20differences%20in%20Mecca%20and%20Medina%20verses.%20The%20Mecca%20verses%20emphasise%2C%20in%20fourteen%20verses%2C%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egeneral%20sense%20of%20a%20lifelong%20discipline%20to%20be%20adopted%20much%20more%20according%20to%20Islamic%20traditions.%20The%20Medina%20verses%20stress%20upon%20a%20sense%20of%20fighting.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20holy%20book%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20believers%20are%20only%20the%20ones%20who%20have%20believed%20in%20Allah%20and%20His%20Messenger%20and%20then%20doubt%20not%20but%20strive%20with%20their%20properties%20and%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20cause%20of%20Allah.%20It%20is%20those%20who%20are%20the%20truthful%E2%80%99%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EQuran%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2049%3A15).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Flies-insistence-and-disregard-for-evidence-the-journey-of-love-jihad-laws%5C%22%3ELies%2C%20Insistence%20and%20Disregard%20for%20Evidence%3A%20The%20Journey%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Laws%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20verses%20on%20jihad%20are%20not%20related%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20either%20war%20or%20violence.%20The%20technical%20word%20used%20for%20fighting%20is%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eqital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3EJihad%20in%20its%20general%20meaning%20refers%20to%20the%20obligation%20on%20all%20Muslims%20to%20follow%20and%20realise%20God%E2%80%99s%20will%20to%20lead%20a%20life%20of%20virtue%20and%20to%20expand%20the%20teachings%20of%20Islam%20through%20preaching%2C%20education%2C%20example%2C%20writing%2C%20etc.%20Jihad%20also%20includes%20the%20right%20and%20the%20obligation%2C%20to%20defend%20Islam%20and%20the%20community%20from%20aggression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20indiscriminate%20use%20of%20the%20term%20by%20Muslim%20extremists%20and%20some%20Muslim%20nations%2C%20that%20have%20displayed%20aggressive%20intentions%20and%20politics%2C%20have%20created%20the%20impression%20for%20common%20non-Muslim%20people%20of%20the%20world%20that%20jihad%20is%20a%20war.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20sense%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20forces%20have%20used%20and%20projected%20jihad%20to%20the%20common%20gullible%20people%2C%20who%20know%20little%20beyond%20a%20ritualistic%20meaning%20about%20their%20own%20religion.%20The%20fear%20is%20thus%20easy%20to%20spawn.%20The%20Muslim%20militants%20have%20not%20helped%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20own%20religion.%20No%20wonder%20reactions%20to%20interfaith%20marriage%20between%20a%20Hindu%20girl%20and%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20are%20sharp%20and%20violent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sociological%20significance%20of%20love%20jihad%20is%20in%20its%20patriarchal%20manifestation.%20For%2C%20%E2%80%98love%E2%80%99%20is%20prefixed%20with%20jihad%20only%20when%20the%20bride%20is%20a%20Hindu%20and%20groom%20a%20Muslim.%20This%20concept%20is%20not%20used%20in%20a%20reverse%20situation%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20bride%20changes%20her%20faith.%20In%20case%20of%20a%20bride%20converting%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20it%20is%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghar%20wapasi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(home%20coming).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20in%20the%20frenzy%20and%20zeal%20to%20%E2%80%98protect%E2%80%99%20Hindu%20girls%20from%20the%20evil%20prowling%20Muslim%20eyes%2C%20not%20only%20the%20vigilante%20justice%2C%20but%20the%20full%20force%20of%20the%20state%20is%20turned%20on%20them%2C%20going%20beyond%20even%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20law.%20Perhaps%20because%20women%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%98property%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20traditional%20Hindu%20household.%C2%A0Most%20feminists%20within%20the%20Hindutva%20fold%20have%20never%20raised%20this%20point%20as%20patriarchy%20surrounding%20families%20takes%20upon%20itself%20the%20role%20of%20being%20the%20guardian.%20Both%2C%20the%20family%20and%20the%20society%2C%20arrogate%20to%20themselves%20the%20right%20to%20decide%20matches%20and%20what%20is%20good%20for%20a%20girl%20in%20matrimonial%20alliance.%E2%80%99Love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20seen%20and%20spoken%20about%20as%20a%20conspiracy%20in%20which%20conversion%20is%20the%20ultimate%20aim%20of%20Muslim%20men.%20This%20bogey%20also%20assumes%20that%20Hindu%20girls%20are%20victims%20because%20they%20have%20been%20coerced%20into%20converting.%20The%20same%20dynamics%20and%20logic%20work%20in%20the%20case%20of%20marriage%20between%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20girl%20and%20a%20Dalit%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConstitutionally%2C%20no%20Indian%20citizen%20can%20be%20prevented%20from%20exercising%20her%2Fhis%20matrimonial%20choice.%20Since%20the%20framers%20of%20the%20constitution%20did%20not%20foresee%20a%20situation%20of%20inter-faith%20marriages%20being%20objected%20to%2C%20and%20jihad%20being%20invoked%20in%20case%20of%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20marriage%2C%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20clause%20dealing%20with%20it.%20However%2C%20Articles%2015%2C%20Article%2025%20and%20others%20relating%20to%20free%20practice%20of%20religion%20provide%20guarantees%20to%20women%20and%20men%20of%20any%20religion%20to%20seek%20inter-faith%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-paper-and-at-odds-with-love-jihad-law-uttarakhands-interfaith-marriage-scheme-still-exists%5C%22%3EOn%20Paper%20and%20At%20Odds%20With%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Law%2C%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Interfaith%20Marriage%20Scheme%20Still%20Exists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20brings%20under%20question%20the%20anti-love%20jihad%20laws%20passed%20by%20states.%20The%20twist%20of%20the%20regimes%2C%20mostly%20headed%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20lies%20in%20%E2%80%98fraudulent%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98forced%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98by%20lure%E2%80%99%20conversions.%20Even%20though%20such%20charges%20are%20not%20easy%20to%20prove%2C%20local%20courts%20have%20been%20pliant%20towards%20the%20government%20and%20their%20police.%20While%20a%20large%20number%20of%20conversions%20have%20not%20been%20reported%2C%20UP%20has%20seen%20conviction%20under%20love-jihad%20laws.%20This%20violates%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20personal%20autonomy%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20the%20apex%20judiciary%20is%20not%20impressed%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20love%20jihad%20and%20the%20laws%20passed%20against%20it.%20A%20major%20test%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3ES%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ehafin%20Jahan%20v.%20Ashokan%20K.M%3C%2Fem%3E.%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20case%20in%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20reversed%20a%20ruling%20in%20favour%20of%20love%20jihad%20issued%20by%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20in%202018.%20In%202021%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Biren%20Vaishnav%20ruled%20that%2C%20%E2%80%98Prima-facie%20inter-faith%20marriages%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults%20by%20operation%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20Section%203%20of%20the%202003%20Act%20interferes%20with%20the%20intricacies%20of%20marriage%20including%20the%20right%20to%20the%20choice%20of%20an%20individual%2C%20thereby%20infringing%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20taken%20a%20strict%20view%20of%20the%20matter%20nor%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20cognizance%20of%20the%20unconstitutionality%20of%20the%20love%20jihad%20laws%20and%20declared%20any%20such%20law%20by%20any%20state%20%3Cem%3Eultra%20vires%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20states%20must%20desist.%20Neither%20the%20number%20of%20inter-faith%20marriages%2C%20nor%20India%E2%80%99s%20demography%20indicate%20any%20danger%20from%20such%20matrimonial%20alliances.%20This%20%E2%80%98otherisation%E2%80%99%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20minority%20must%20stop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20is%20a%20political%20scientist.%20He%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21%20and%20Principal%2C%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Evening%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%20(2018).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692268588000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17160453%2Fc6e7db8f-74ee-43fd-8bc8-583eba8ef9ff.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20majority%20of%20the%20verses%20in%20the%20Quran%20on%20jihad%20are%20not%20related%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20either%20war%20or%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20posts%20breezy%20new%20pics%20amid%20toxic%20talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692268375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102802299%2Cimgsize-117623.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famidst-talks-that-her-marriage-to-ranbir-kapoor-is-toxic-alia-bhatt-posts-breezy-new-pics-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F102802447.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102802447.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20recently%20came%20under%20fire%20when%20she%20said%20that%20her%20husband