ped.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20not%20say%20what%20precisely%20his%20government%20was%20doing%20to%20ensure%20justice%20in%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2031%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20provide%20a%20complete%20break-up%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUpdated-status-report-on-WPC-No.-540-and-connected-cases-before-SC.pdf%5C%22%3E5995%20First%20Information%20Reports%20%5BFIRs%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20the%20Manipur%20government%20claimed%20to%20have%20registered%20during%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20State%2C%C2%A0including%20cases%20of%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20arson%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20burning%20of%20villages%2C%20homes%20and%20places%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20July%204%2C%20the%20petition%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20violence%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20approximately%20142%20people%20and%20the%20displacement%20of%20approximately%2055%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Who%20Gains%20and%20Who%20Loses%3F%20A%20Report%20From%20Manipur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-gains-and-who-loses-a-report-from-manipur%5C%22%3EWho%20Gains%20and%20Who%20Loses%3F%20A%20Report%20From%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20report%20presented%20in%20court%20also%20mentions%20the%20viral%20video%20case%20%E2%80%93%20stating%20that%20the%20two%20women%20were%20gang-raped%20and%20their%20father%20and%20brother%20were%20killed%20by%20a%20mob%20on%20May%204.%20While%20the%20Zero%20FIR%20in%20this%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20May%2018%20%E2%80%93%2014%20days%20after%20the%20incident%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20only%20on%20July%2024%20that%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20statements%20were%20recorded%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%E2%80%99s%20General%20Secretary%20and%20CPI%20leader%20Annie%20Raja%2C%20who%20was%20also%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98fact-finding%20committee%E2%80%99%20to%20probe%20the%20ground%20reality%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20violence%20and%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%2C%20had%20the%20government%20intervened%20on%20time.%20%E2%80%9COur%20report%20also%20clearly%20spells%20that%20the%20government%20had%20an%20agenda%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%20to%20pit%20the%20two%20communities%20at%20loggerheads%20so%20that%20they%20refuse%20to%20coexist.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20we%20could%20see%20that%20Meitei%20women%20themselves%20had%20become%20part%20of%20the%20crimes%20against%20Kuki%20women%2C%20alongside%20men.%20It%20is%20a%20major%20failure%20of%20the%20government%20which%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20brutality%20Kuki%20women%20have%20experienced%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raja%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20review%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20status%20report%20and%20the%20writ%20petition%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20about%20the%20gravity%20of%20crimes%20that%20women%20have%20faced%20during%20the%20three-month-long%20and%20continuing%20ethnic%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20report%20discloses%20several%20cases%20where%20women%20have%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20several%20cases%20mentioned%2C%20in%20a%20case%20of%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20of%20two%20women%20in%20Imphal%20East%20on%20May%204%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20arrest%20till%20date%3B%20nor%20has%20there%20been%20any%20detention%20in%20another%20case%20of%20gang-rape%20where%20an%2018-year-old%20woman%20came%20forward%20to%20narrate%20the%20ordeal%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%20at%20the%20Kangpokpi%20police%20station%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20described%20how%20she%20was%20first%20abducted%20and%20assaulted%20by%20four%20men%20in%20Imphal%20East%20on%20May%2015.%20According%20to%20the%20status%20report%2C%20three%20men%20raped%20her%20there.%20In%20her%20complaint%20filed%20at%20the%20Kangpokpi%20Police%20Station%2C%20she%20has%20detailed%20how%20she%20was%20abducted%20and%20tortured%20by%20at%20least%204-5%20men%20who%20hit%20with%20the%20butt%20of%20their%20guns.%20They%20issued%20multiple%20threats%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%20while%20scouting%20for%20a%20location%20to%20kill%20her.%20She%20begged%20them%20to%20spare%20her%20and%20promised%20the%20men%20that%20she%20will%20never%20return%20to%20Imphal%20if%20they%20let%20her%20go%20and%20she%20just%20wants%20to%20meet%20her%20parents.%20She%20was%20later%20dragged%20out%20of%20the%20car%2C%20physically%20assaulted%20and%20gang%20raped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20P.S.%20Kangpokpi%20on%20July%2021%2C%20pursuant%20to%20which%20a%20Zero%20FIR%20was%20registered%20on%2021.07.2023%20under%20Secs.%20376%3B%20376D%3B%20354%3B%20307%3B%20364%3B%20506%3B%2043%20IPC%20and%20Sec%203%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%20However%2C%20the%20petition%20claims%20that%20she%20has%20not%20been%20contacted%20by%20the%20police%20and%20has%20received%20no%20updates%20on%20the%20investigation%20or%20arrests.%20She%20has%20also%20not%20received%20any%20compensation%20from%20the%20government.%20She%20is%20currently%20staying%20at%20the%20Leicob%20relief%20camp%20with%20her%20family.%20She%20is%20very%20weak%2C%20traumatised%20and%20requires%20psychological%20counselling.%20The%20family%20also%20requires%20urgent%20rehabilitation%20since%20their%20house%20in%20Imphal%20was%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20case%2C%20two%20Kuki-Zo%20women%20who%20were%20out%20on%20May%204%20for%20work%20lost%20contact%20with%20their%20families%20later%20in%20the%20afternoon%20and%20could%20not%20be%20contacted%20later.%20Later%2C%20the%20family%20of%20these%20women%20learnt%20from%20a%20medical%20staffer%20that%20the%20two%20women%20aged%2024%20and%2021%20were%20gangraped%20allegedly%20by%20a%20Meitei%20mob.%20The%20family%20also%20learnt%20from%20a%20co-worker%20of%20these%20women%20that%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20100%20Meitei%20men%2C%20who%20came%20to%20their%20place%20of%20work%2C%20demanding%20to%20know%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20two%20Kuki-Zo%20women%20who%20worked%20there.%20The%20two%20women%20were%20dragged%20into%20a%20room%20where%20for%20almost%20two%20hours%20they%20were%20tortured%2C%20raped%20and%20subsequently%20murdered%20by%20the%20mob%20of%20Meiti%20men.%20While%20they%20have%20heard%20unverified%20reports%20that%20a%20postmortem%20has%20been%20conducted%2C%20no%20government%20official%20has%20contacted%20them%20to%20provide%20clear%20and%20accurate%20information.%20The%20informational%20vacuum%20that%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20living%20in%20has%20intensified%20their%20anguish%20and%20despair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20situations%20of%20conflict%20exacerbate%20and%20amplify%20the%20gender-based%20violence%20faced%20by%20women%20as%20their%20bodies%20are%20perceived%20as%20repositories%20of%20community%20%E2%80%9Chonour%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20well%20documented.%20In%20the%20present%20situation%2C%20women%20from%20the%20minority%2C%20tribal%20and%20marginalised%20Kuki-Zo%20community%2C%20viewed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%2C%20were%20targeted%20by%20mobs%20of%20the%20dominant%20community%2C%20the%20petition%20has%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%2C%20WGI%2C%20founded%20in%202009%2C%20is%20a%20network%20of%20academics%2C%20social%20workers%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20activists%20who%20have%20been%20engaging%20actively%20on%20issues%20impacting%20the%20lives%20of%20women%2C%20more%20particularly%20the%20security%20of%20women%20in%20the%20conflict%20prone%20regions%20in%20the%20states%20of%20North%20East%20and%20strengthening%20the%20capacity%20of%