20a%20lone%20wind%20turbine%20technician%20hanging%20on%20the%20side%20of%20a%20wind%20turbine%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Portugal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dde1c2bd8c0900184ed1e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221919%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20wind%20turbine%20technician%20on%20the%20job.%3Cp%3EMariana%20Castelo%20Branco%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20stock%20market%20has%20been%20boosted%20by%20a%20surge%20in%20tech%20shares%20this%20year%2C%20thanks%20to%20investor%20excitement%20over%20AI.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20two%20fund%20managers%20see%20a%20massive%20investment%20opportunity%20outside%20the%20technology%20craze%3A%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGlobal%20energy%20transition%20will%20need%20%26quot%3Bcomfortably%20%24100%20trillion%26quot%3B%20in%20capital%20over%20the%20next%20thirty%20years%2C%20says%20Mark%20Lacy%20of%20Schroders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20transition%20toward%20clean%20energy%20will%20create%20investment%20opportunities%20worth%20at%20least%20%24100%20trillion%20over%20the%20coming%20three%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20two%20fund%20managers%20at%20Schroders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20investor%20excitement%20this%20year%20has%20mostly%20centered%20around%20the%20capabilities%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20technology%2C%20Mark%20Lacy%20and%20David%20Boyce%20see%20enormous%20potential%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schroders.com%2Fen%2Fglobal%2Findividual%2Finsights%2Fthe-100-trillion-opportunity-for-energy-investors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20on%20The%20Investor%20Download%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Lacy%20said%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bcomfortably%20over%20%242%20trillion%20per%20annum%26quot%3B%20feeding%20into%20the%20energy%20transition%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20outside%20of%20the%20traditional%20oil%20and%20gas%20market%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20cumulative%20comfortably%20of%20%24100%20trillion%20over%20the%202020%20to%202050%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%20has%20the%20energy%20market%20from%20a%20public%20perspective%20or%20a%20private%20perspective%20ever%20seen%20this%20much%20capital%20that's%20needed%20going%20into%20it%20in%20a%2030%20year%20period.%20So%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20transformational%20from%20an%20infrastructure%20perspective%2C%20but%20also%20from%20an%20investment%20perspective.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Schroders%20fund%20managers%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20uptick%20in%20green%20energy%20investment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwhy-clean-energy-stocks-lost-out-last-week-1032412814%5C%22%3Ethe%20International%20Energy%20Association%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20capital%20investment%20flowing%20into%20the%20solar%20sector%20is%20set%20to%20overtake%20the%20amount%20in%20oil%20production%20for%20the%20first%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IEA%2C%20solar%20investments%20are%20expected%20to%20top%20%241%20billion%20a%20day%20in%202023%20with%20over%20%241.7%20trillion%20slated%20to%20flow%20into%20clean-energy%20technologies%20such%20as%20EVs%2C%20renewables%20and%20storage.%20Overall%2C%20global%20investment%20in%20energy%20is%20projected%20to%20hit%20about%20%242.8%20trillion%20in%20the%20current%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20every%20dollar%20invested%20in%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20about%201.7%20dollars%20are%20now%20going%20into%20clean%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20Fatih%20Birol%2C%20the%20IEA's%20executive%20director%2C%20told%20CNBC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmar