.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-marks-his-first-anniversary-of-signing-of-major-climate-health-and-tax-law%2Farticleshow%2F102800115.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-marks-his-first-anniversary-of-signing-of-major-climate-health-and-tax-law%2Famp_articleshow%2F102800115.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-marks-his-first-anniversary-of-signing-of-major-climate-health-and-tax-law%2Famp_articleshow%2F102800115.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starbucks'%20%241.25%20cold%20foam%20is%20the%20chain's%20most%20popular%20drinks%20add-on%2C%20and%20one%20of%20its%20most%20expensive.%20This%20is%20how%20it's%20made.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20Starbucks%20cold%20drinks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d4fc804dd2b50019c2d73f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECold%20foam%20is%20now%20Starbucks'%20most%20popular%20beverage%20modification.%3Cp%3EStarbucks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECold%20foam%20is%20now%20Starbucks'%20most%20popular%20beverage%20modification.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt's%20made%20by%20frothing%20nonfat%20cold%20milk%20and%20is%20added%20to%20iced%20drinks%20like%20cold%20brews.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%241.25%20add-on%20was%20first%20rolled%20out%20at%20regular%20Starbucks%20stores%20in%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can't%20get%20enough%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-cold-drinks-are-hotter-than-ever-2023-8%5C%22%3EStarbucks'%20cold%20foam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20now%20the%20coffee%20chain's%20most%20popular%20add-on%2C%20and%20it's%20pushing%20up%20the%20Siren's%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bvelvety%26quot%3B%20foam%20is%20made%20by%20frothing%20nonfat%20cold%20milk%20%26quot%3Buntil%20it%20is%20smooth%2C%20creating%20layers%20of%20creamy%20texture%20and%20flavor%20without%20the%20cream%2C%26quot%3B%20Starbucks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstories.starbucks.com%2Fpress%2F2018%2Fintroducing-cold-foam-at-starbucks%2F%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fathome.starbucks.com%2Frecipe%2Fao-july-aug21%2Fvanilla-sweet-cream-cold-foam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20sweet-vanilla%20cold%20foam%20on%20Starbucks'%20website%20says%20that%20customers%20can%20make%20it%20at%20home%20by%20frothing%20cold%20milk%20with%20powdered%20sugar%20and%20vanilla%20extract.%20For%20a%20one-person%20serving%2C%20it%20suggests%20using%20a%20quarter-cup%20of%202%25%20milk%2C%20a%20tablespoon%20of%20powdered%20sugar%2C%20and%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20teaspoon%20of%20vanilla%20extract.%20A%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcooking.nytimes.com%2Frecipes%2F1024281-sweet-cream-cold-foam%5C%22%3Erecipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20using%20heaving%20whipping%20cream%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ideal%20cold%20foam%20is%20both%20fluffy%20and%20pourable%3B%20it%20seeps%20gradually%20into%20your%20preferred%20coffee%20drink%20or%20iced%20beverage%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20article%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epicurious.com%2Fshopping%2Fhow-to-cold-foam-at-home%5C%22%3EEpicurious%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20adds%20a%20sumptuous%2C%20creamy%20texture%20to%20any%20beverage%2C%20and%20often%20doubles%20as%20a%20vehicle%20for%20sweeteners%20and%20flavorings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cold%20foam%20can%20be%20served%20on%20top%20of%20cold%20coffees%20that%20already%20have%20milk%20in%20them%2C%20or%20can%20add%20a%20splash%20of%20dairy%20to%20a%20black%20iced%20coffee.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epicurious.com%2Fshopping%2Fhow-to-cold-foam-at-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEpicurious%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20though%20you%20can%20use%20substitute%20the%20milk%20with%20non-dairy%20milk%2C%20whole%20milk%2C%20or%20heavy%20cream%2C%20skim%20milk%20works%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20first%20debuted%20cold%20foam%20when%20it%20opened%20its%20Reserve%20Roastery%20in%20Seattle%20in%20December%202014%2C%20but%20the%20foam%20wasn't%20introduced%20to%20its%20regular%20coffee%20stores%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstories.starbucks.com%2Fpress%2F2018%2Fintroducing-cold-foam-at-starbucks%2F%5C%22%3EApril%202018%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20drinks%20come%20with%20cold%20foam%20on%20top%20as%20standard%2C%20such%20as%20some%20of%20its%20flavored%20cold%20brews%2C%20customers%20can%20opt%20to%20add%20it%20to%20other%20cold%20drinks%20for%20%241.25.%20The%20price%20stays%20the%20same%20regardless%20of%20whether%20you%20order%20Starbucks'%20biggest%20drink%20size%2C%20at%2030%20fluid%20ounces%2C%20or%20smallest%2C%20at%2012%20fluid%20ounces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20chain's%20other%20customizations%2C%20including%20adding%20a%20flavored%20drizzle%2C%20sprinkles%2C%20chai%2C%20syrup%2C%20or%20extra%20shot%20of%20espresso.%20The%20only%20modification%20that%20appears%20to%20cost%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20adding%20cold%20foam%20is%20substituting%20the%20milk%20with%20vanilla%20sweet%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%20there%20are%20six%20flavors%20of%20cold%20foam%20available%20%E2%80%93%20chocolate%20cream%2C%20cinnamon%20sweet%20cream%2C%20matcha%20cream%2C%20salted%20caramel%20cream%2C%20vanilla%20sweet%20cream%2C%20and%20white%20chocolate%20macadamia%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foam%20has%20been%20a%20massive%20success%20for%20the%20coffee%20company.%20It's%20featured%20in%20a%20number%20of%20customized%20beverages%20that%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20TikTok%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-tiktok-drink-iced-white-mocha-cold-foam-caramel-drizzle-2021-7%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%228660206fcd018194a041bc19f2599034%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-tiktok-drink-iced-white-mocha-cold-foam-caramel-drizzle-2021-7%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3Eiced%20white%20mochas%20with%20vanilla%20sweet%20cream%20cold%20foam%20and%20extra%20caramel%20drizzle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20perhaps%20because%20it%20provides%20an%20attractive%20layered%20appearance.%20It%20was%20also%20included%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-is-testing-a-way-to-order-social-media-drinks-2021-6%5C%22%3EPink%20Drink%20Remixed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20on%20a%20viral%20beverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20has%20even%20rolled%20out%20handheld%20cold%20foam%20blenders%20to%20all%20its%20US%20company-operated%20stores%20so%20that%20baristas%20can%20make%20it%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20isn't%20the%20only%20place%20you%20can%20get%20cold%20foam%20on%20your%20drink.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-chains-see-sales-cold-drinks-surge-thanks-gen-z-2023-8%5C%22%3ETim%20Hortons%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20for%20example%2C%20sells%20set%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timhortons.com%2Fmenu%2Fpicker-03e2ca28-45dc-46d5-9bb2-de1d7c7ae293%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echilled%20drinks%20with%20cold%20foam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20also%20has%20the%20option%20for%20customers%20to%20add%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timhortons.com%2Fmenu%2Fpicker-80f0d845-fe0d-435e-9581-05c3eeb9023e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20of%20its%20other%20cold%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDunkin'%20started%20selling%20sweet%20cold%20foam%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%