ednesday%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20can%20never%20take%20away%20the%20gigantic%20contributions%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%20the%20country's%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20his%20official%20handle%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20posted%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20today%2C%20an%20iconic%20institution%20gets%20a%20new%20name.%20The%20world-renowned%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20becomes%20PMML-Prime%20Ministers'%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library.%20Mr%20Modi%20possesses%20a%20huge%20bundle%20of%20fears%2C%20complexes%20and%20insecurities%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20our%20first%20and%20longest-serving%20Prime%20Minister.%20He%20has%20had%20a%20single-point%20agenda%20of%20denying%2C%20distorting%2C%20defaming%20and%20destroying%20Nehru%20and%20the%20Nehruvian%20legacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20was%20officially%20renamed%20the%20Prime%20Ministers'%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(PMML)%20by%20the%20Centre%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice%20Chairman%20of%20PMML's%20Executive%20Council%20A%20Surya%20Prakash%20yesterday%20said%20the%20new%20museum%20showcases%20the%20achievements%20and%20the%20contributions%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20to%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20visiting%20the%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20can%20see%20how%20we%20have%20showcased%20Nehru%2C%20his%20temples%20of%20modern%20India%2C%20the%20Hirakud%20Dam%2C%20Nagarajuna%20Sagar%20Dam%2C%20his%20idea%20of%20setting%20up%20institutes%20of%20technology%2C%20and%20Planning%20Commission%20in%20his%2017-year%20tenure%20as%20PM%20at%20the%20Teen%20Murti%20Bhavan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20over%20the%20renaming%20of%20the%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20said%20that%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20only%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20his%20family%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20basic%20difference%20between%20the%20thinking%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20and%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi.%20They%20(Congress)%20think%20that%20only%20Nehru%20ji%20and%20the%20family%20matters.%20Narendra%20Modi%20gave%20a%20respectful%20position%20to%20all%20the%20PMs%20of%20the%20country%20at%20the%20museum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20mid-June%2C%20during%20a%20special%20meeting%20of%20the%20NMML%20Society%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20its%20name%20will%20be%20changed%20to%20PMML%20Society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20special%20meeting%20of%20the%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20Society%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20the%20Vice-President%20of%20the%20Society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692264300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F023amhm8_rahul-gandhi_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-memorial-museum-and-library-rahul-gandhi-how-rahul-gandhi-responded-to-renaming-of-nehru-museum-and-library-4305215%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20controversy%20around%20the%20renaming%20of%20the%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20to%20Prime%20Ministers'%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(PMML)%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20today%20said%20he%20was%20known%20more%20for%20his%20work%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-memorial-museum-and-library-rahul-gandhi-how-rahul-gandhi-responded-to-renaming-of-nehru-museum-and-library-4305215%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%