%20from%20organised%20crime%2C%20including%20plush%20bungalows%20in%20the%20most%20sought-after%20addresses%2C%20bundles%20of%20cash%2C%20luxury%20cars%2C%20jewellery%2C%20handbags%20and%20gold%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20money-laundering%20cases%2C%20police%20said%20400%20officers%20fanned%20out%20across%20Singapore%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20launched%20simultaneous%20raids%20on%20residences%20across%20the%20city-state%2C%20from%20the%20Orchard%20Road%20shopping%20belt%20to%20the%20resort%20island%20of%20Sentosa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20on%20at%20least%20nine%20locations%20netted%20assets%20totalling%20a%20staggering%20S%241%20billion%2C%20police%20said.%20These%20included%2094%20properties%2C%20bank%20accounts%20with%20S%24110%20million%2C%2050%20vehicles%2C%20stacks%20of%20cash%20amounting%20to%20more%20than%20S%2423%20million%2C%20hundreds%20of%20luxury%20handbags%20and%20watches%2C%20fistfuls%20of%20jewellery%20and%20two%20gold%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20foreigners%20aged%20between%2031%20and%2044%20were%20arrested%2C%20including%20one%20man%20who%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20second-floor%20balcony%20of%20his%20bungalow%20in%20a%20tony%20neighbourhood%20and%20was%20found%20hiding%20in%20a%20drain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20a%2040-year-old%20Cypriot%20national%2C%20sustained%20injuries%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital.%20From%20his%20home%2C%20police%20seized%20cash%20amounting%20to%20more%20than%20S%242.1%20million%2C%20four%20bank%20accounts%20with%20more%20than%20S%246.7%20million%20and%20ownership%20documents%20of%2013%20properties%20and%20five%20vehicles%20with%20an%20estimated%20value%20of%20more%20than%20S%24118%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20arrested%20people%20included%20citizens%20from%20China%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20Cyprus%20and%20Vanuatu.%20One%20woman%20was%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwelve%20people%20were%20assisting%20police%20in%20their%20investigations%20while%20another%20eight%20were%20wanted.%20Police%20said%20all%20those%20in%20the%20case%20were%20foreigners%20and%20were%20linked%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20statement%20said%20the%20group%20was%20suspected%20to%20be%20laundering%20proceeds%20from%20overseas%20organised%20crime%2C%20including%20scams%20and%20online%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Monetary%20Authority%20of%20Singapore%20said%20it%20takes%20this%20case%20seriously%20and%20has%20contacted%20the%20financial%20institutions%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20potentially%20tainted%20funds%20have%20been%20identified%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Chew%2C%20director%20of%20commercial%20affairs%20at%20the%20police%20force%2C%20said%20Singapore%20has%20%26quot%3Bzero%20tolerance%26quot%3B%20for%20being%20used%20as%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20criminals%20or%20their%20families%20and%20for%20banking%20facilities%20to%20be%20abused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20message%20to%20these%20criminals%20is%20simple%20-%20if%20we%20catch%20you%2C%20we%20will%20arrest%20you.%20If%20we%20find%20your%20ill-gotten%20gains%2C%20we%20will%20seize%20them.%20We%20will%20deal%20with%20you%20to%20the%20fullest%20extent%20of%20our%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore%20has%20in%20recent%20years%20seen%20an%20influx%20of%20foreign%20money.%20Latest%20figures%20from%20the%20central%20bank%20show%20that%20total%20assets%20under%20management%20in%20Singapore%20rose%2016%25%20in%202021%20to%20S%245.4%20trillion%2C%20compared%20with%20a%20global%20increase%20of%2012%25%20to%20%24112%20trillion%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692263040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbvklgcig_singapore-money-laundering-case_625x300_17_August_23.