uot%3B%20said%20CoTU's%20Media%20Cell%20Coordinator%2C%20Ng.%20Lun%20Kipgen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20supply%20chain%20of%20essential%20commodities%20from%20Imphal%20valley%20towards%20the%20hill%20areas%2C%20particularly%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Tengnoupal%20and%20Moreh%2C%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bstalled%20by%20mobs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssuing%20an%20ultimatum%2C%20Mr%20Kipgen%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20this%2C%20CoTU%20felt%20that%20this%20prescriptive%20policy%20to%20placate%20one%20community%20over%20the%20other%20by%20the%20Centre%20needs%20to%20be%20considered.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20public%20will%20be%20compelled%20to%20impose%20a%20highway%20blockade%20if%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20fails%20to%20check%20the%20selective%20blockade%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20valley%20within%20three%20days%2C%20with%20effect%20from%20August%2017%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20180%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20more%20than%203%2C000%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20began%20on%20May%203%2C%20when%20a%20'Tribal%20Solidarity%20March'%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2060%2C000%20people%20remain%20displaced%20and%20property%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20has%20been%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692262620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fq20ig8g_imphal-west-manipur_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-block-highways-in-3-days-unless-manipur-tribal-group-issues-ultimatum-4305125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alleging%20that%20there%20is%20a%20selective%20blockade%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20preventing%20essential%20items%20from%20reaching%20the%20hills%2C%20a%20tribal%20group%20has%20threatened%20to%20block%20