tudents%2C%20academics%20and%20even%20its%20own%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20significant%20given%20how%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-resigns-as-professor-at-ashoka-university%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%252520a%252520letter%252520to%252520students%2CVC%252520rather%252520than%252520stop%252520writing.%5C%22%3Enudged%20and%20persuaded%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20reputed%20political%20science%20professor%20and%20former%20vice%20chancellor%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%20to%20resign%20in%20March%202021%20due%20to%20his%20media%20writings%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20science%20faculty%20said%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGillesVerniers%2Fstatus%2F1692033163697033714%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20%E2%80%9Cby%20now%2C%20the%20pattern%20is%20all%20too%20familiar%2C%20especially%20for%20us%20as%20a%20department%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20that%20the%20alleged%20attempt%20by%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Froles%2Fleadership-team%2F%3Ffilterby%3D320%5C%22%3Egoverning%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinvestigate%E2%80%9D%20Das%E2%80%99s%20research%20has%20created%20a%20climate%20of%20fear%20amongst%20the%20academic%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20governing%20body.%20Through%20its%20interference%20and%20suggestion%20of%20constituting%20a%20committee%2C%20the%20governing%20body%20has%20questioned%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20peer%20review%20system%20and%20in%20effect%20has%20cast%20aspersions%20against%20scholars%20at%20Ashoka%20and%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continues%3A%20%E2%80%9CFurthermore%2C%20the%20governing%20body%E2%80%99s%20actions%20have%20signalled%20to%20students%20that%20critical%20enquiry%20can%20be%20met%20with%20severe%20repercussions%20and%20thus%20undermines%20the%20work%20that%20we%20do%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20classroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20illiberal%20action%20by%20a%20leading%20liberal%20arts%20university%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20as%20a%20bastion%20of%20critical%20thinking%2C%20creates%20a%20climate%20of%20fear%20amongst%20the%20academic%20community%20and%20casts%20severe%20doubt%20on%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20academic%20freedom%20and%20critical%20enquiry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fashoka-university-facultys-research-paper-on-bjp-manipulation-in-2019-election-triggers-row%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20Ashoka%20University%20Professor%E2%80%99s%20Paper%20on%20BJP%20%E2%80%98Manipulation%E2%80%99%20in%202019%20Election%20Actually%20Says%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaculty%20from%20Ashoka%E2%80%99s%20economics%20department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fecon-dept-says-ashoka-governing-body-interference-forcing-scholars-to-operate-in-environment-of-fear%5C%22%3Ewere%20the%20first%20to%20accuse%20the%20governing%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%98investigate%E2%80%99%20the%20merits%20of%20Das%E2%80%99s%20research.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20governing%20body%20but%20has%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Das%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20economist%20Pulapre%20Balakrishnan%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fsecond-professor-quits-as-democratic-backsliding-row-continues-to-roil-ashoka-university%5C%22%3Ealso%20resigned%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20his%20tenured%20post%20at%20Ashoka%2C%20in%20what%20sources%20have%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20an%20act%20of%20solidarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwit