2C%20August%2014%2C%20at%20its%20regional%20office%20in%20Ranchi%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%20However%2C%20he%20gave%20it%20a%20miss%2C%20alleging%20that%20summons%20is%20%E2%80%9Cactuated%20by%20malice%20and%20is%20part%20of%20the%20political%20conspiracy%20to%20destabilise%20the%20democratically%20elected%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fmoney-laundering-case-jharkhand-chief-minister-hemant-soren-threatens-legal-action-on-enforcement-directorate-for-summon%2Fcid%2F1959494%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-summons-jharkhand-cm-soren-again-in-yet-another-alleged-money-laundering-case%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20called%20for%20questioning%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20an%20alleged%20defence%20land%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20summons%20was%20issued%20to%20him%20on%20August%207.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20for%20the%20second%20time%20that%20Soren%20had%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20central%20agency%20in%20connection%20with%20money%20laundering%20cases%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20time.%20He%20had%20also%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20last%20November%20in%20connection%20with%20another%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20illegal%20mining%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%2C%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20summons%20and%20the%20day%20he%20was%20called%20in%20for%20questioning.%20%E2%80%9CYour%20choice%20of%20the%20date%20does%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20the%20undersigned%20%5BSoren%5D.%20You%20and%20your%20political%20masters%20are%20fully%20aware%20that%20being%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20undersigned%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hoist%20the%20National%20Flag%E2%80%A6.%20Preparations%20for%20the%20Independence%20Day%20function%20start%20a%20week%20before%20and%20August%2014%20is%20an%20important%20day%20for%20the%20same%20when%20many%20meetings%20are%20pre-scheduled%E2%80%A6.%20The%20captioned%20summons%E2%80%A6%20is%20deliberate%20and%20part%20of%20the%20design%20to%20besmirch%20the%20reputation%20not%20only%20of%20the%20undersigned%20but%20also%20the%20elected%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soren%20said%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20he%20addressed%20to%20Deovrat%20Jha%2C%20ED%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Ranchi%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20warn%20the%20probe%20agency%20of%20legal%20action%20if%20summons%20issued%20to%20him%20is%20not%20withdrawn.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20undersigned%20calls%20upon%20you%20to%20forthwith%20withdraw%20the%20captioned%20summons%20failing%20which%2C%20the%20undersigned%20shall%20be%20constrained%20to%20seek%20legal%20remedies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20mincing%20words%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%E2%80%9D%20only%20because%20he%20does%20not%20align%20with%20the%20party%20ruling%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20central%20agencies%20have%20been%20targeting%20the%20undersigned%20for%20over%20a%20year%20now%20only%20because%20the%20undersigned%20is%20not%20aligned%20with%20the%20political%20party%20which%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20earlier%20summons%2C%20of%20November%202022%2C%20Soren%20notes%20that%20he%20has%20already%20provided%20details%20of%20all%20movable%20and%20immovable%20properties%20owned%20by%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members%20along%20with%20certified%20copies%20of%20the%20title%20deeds.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20has%20already%20furnished%20details%20of%20his%20bank%20account%20and%20permanent%20account%20number%20(PAN)%20number.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20he%20was%20questioned%20for%20over%2010%20hours%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20mining%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20also%20referred%20to%20an%20instance%20from%202020%20where%20the%20Lokpal%20directed%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20conduct%20an%20enquiry%20against%20his%20father%2C%20Shibu%20Soren%2C%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20filed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20such%20enquiry%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20wrongfully%20and%20illegally%20carried%20out%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20immovable%20assets%20owned%20by%20the%20undersigned.%20It%20may%20be%20in%20your%20interest%20to%20obtain%20a%20report%20from%20CBI%20on%20the%20undersigned%E2%80%99s%20immovable%20assets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2014%2C%20a%20person%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20regional%20office%20of%20the%20ED%20on%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20behalf%20and%20submitted%20a%20sealed%20envelope%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhemant-soren-skips-enforcement-directorates-summons-in-land-grabbing-case-2421308-2023-08-15%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692250377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17105007%2FF3jBZdiXEAA99Q2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwithdraw-summons-forthwith-jharkhand-cm-soren-warns-ed-of-legal-action%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20was%20asked%20to%20depose%20on%20August%2014%20at%20the%20central%20agency's%20office%20in%20Ranchi%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20which%20he%20gave%20it%20a%20miss.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwithdraw-summons-forthwith-jharkhand-cm-soren-warns-ed-of-legal-action%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Imphal%20Out%20of%20Bounds%20for%20Kuki-Zos%2C'%2010%20MLAs%20Urge%20PM%20to%20Create%20DGP%2C%20Chief%20Secy%20Posts%20for%20Hills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20162818%2Fimphal-long-shot-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ten%20Kuki-Zomi%20MLAs%20of%20Manipur%20have%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20requesting%20that%20posts%20of%20chief%20secretary%20and%20director%20general%20of%20police%20or%20its%20equivalents%20be%20created%20for%20the%20five%20hill%20districts%20where%20members%20of%20the%20community%20are%20residing%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signatories%20have%20also%20asked%20for%20the%20sanction%20of%20Rs%20500%20crores%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Relief%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20of%20the%20signatories%20are%20BJP%20MLAs.%20These%20MLAs%20are%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-kuki-zomi-mlas-separate-administration%5C%22%3Esame%3C%2Fa%3E%20ones%20who%20had%20pressed%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20Kuki-Zomi%20residents%20of%20Manipur.%20Chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-naga-mlas-biren-singh-kuki-separate-administration%5C%22%3Elikely%20to%20move%20a%20resolution%20to%20preserve%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20integrity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20thus%20go%20against%20this%20demand%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20on%20August%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signatory%20MLAs%20and%20their%20constituencies%20are%20parties%20are%20as%20follows%3A%20Haokholet%20Kipgen%20(Saitu%2C%20independent)%2C%20Letpao%20Haokip%20(Tengnoupal%2C%20BJP)%2C%20L.M.%20Kaute%20(Churachandpur%2C%20BJP)%2C%20Nemcha%20Kipgen%20(Kangpokpi%2C%20BJP)%2C%20Ngursanglur%20Sanate%20(Tipaimukh%2C%20BJP)%2C%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20(Saikot%2C%20BJP)%2C%20Chinlunthang%20(Singhat%2C%20KPA)%2C%20Letzamang%20Haokip%20(Henglep%2C%20BJP)%2C%20Kimneo%20Haokip%20Hangshing%20(Saikul%2C%20KPA)%20and%20Vungzagin%20Valte%20(Thanlon%2C%20BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDated%20August%2016%2C%20the%20memorandum%20says%20that%20since%20May%203%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cdevastating%20attacks%20by%20the%20Meitei%20militias%2C%20viz%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20along%20with%20Meitei%20mobs%20in%20Greater%20Imphal%20area%E2%80%9D%20on%20Kuki-Zomis%20living%20in%20Imphal%20as%20government%20employees%2C%20businessmen%2C%20daily%20wage%20earners%20and%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20lists%20several%20incidents%20where%20Kuki-Zomi%20people%20were%20allegedly%20tortured%2C%20molested%2C%20raped%20and%20killed.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20members%20of%20the%20State%20Legislative%20Assembly%20were%20not%20spared%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20attack%20on%20Thanlon%20MLA%20Vungzagin%20Valte%20who%20was%20beaten%20and%20left%20for%20dead.%20Valte%E2%80%99s%20driver%20was%20killed.%20Two%20cabinet%20ministers%E2%80%99%20houses%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20them%20are%20signatories%20%E2%80%93%20were%20%E2%80%9Cburnt%20to%20ashes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20memorandum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20continues%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwage%20war%20against%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20hill%20tribals%20by%20attacking%20villages%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20call%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20%E2%80%9Ca%20state-sponsored%20war%20against%20Kuki-Zo%20tribals%2C%E2%80%9D%20citing%20several%20instances%20where%20CM%20Biren%20and%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20leaders%20have%20allegedly%20called%20for%20violence%20against%20Kuki-Zomi%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20can%20go%20to%20Imphal%2C%20nor%20government%20employees%20posted%20in%20Imphal%20capital%20and%20other%20valley%20districts%20can%20attend%20their%20offices%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20it%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%5BE%5Dven%20IAS%20and%20MCS%20officers%2C%20and%20IPS%20and%20MPS%20officer%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20function%20and%20discharge%20their%20duties%20as%20Imphal%20Valley%20has%20also%20become%20a%20valley%20of%20death%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20signatories%20ask%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%5BI%5Dn%20order%20to%20solve%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20the%20government%20employees%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribals%20and%20for%20efficient%20administration%20of%20the%20districts%20inhabited%20by%20us%2C%20the%20post%20of%20Chief%20Secretary%20or%20its%20equivalent%20post%20and%20the%20post%20of%20DGP%20or%20equivalent%20post%20need%20to%20be%20immediately%20created.%20Besides%2C%20other%20key%20senior%20level%20posts%20in%20the%20civil%20and%20police%20department%20should%20also%20be%20created%20in%20public%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20districts%20where%20the%2010%20MLAs%20have%20asked%20for%20high-ranking%20officials%20are%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Chandel%2C%20Tengnoupal%20and%20Pherzaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20June%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20had%20appointed%20Rajiv%20Singh%2C%20a%20Tripura-cadre%20IPS%20officer%20as%20the%20new%20Manipur%20DGP.%20The%20incumbent%2C%20P.%20Doungel%2C%20was%20made%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(Home)%2C%20which%20was%20a%20post%20created%20overnight.%20Notably%2C%20Doungel%20is%20a%20prominent%20Kuki%20community%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Wilson%20Hangshing%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20(KPA)%2C%20two%20MLAs%20from%20which%20have%20also%20signed%20the%20memorandum%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20legitimate%20demand%20considering%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20access%20even%20the%20Imphal%20airport.%20Those%20from%20Churachandpur%20are%20motoring%20down%20a%20long%20way%20to%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20to%20take%20a%20flight%20out%20of%20Manipur%3B%20the%20Kukis%20from%20Kangpokpi%20are%20driving%20down%20to%20Nagaland%20to%20take%20a%20flight.%20One%20takes%20the%20whole%20day%20while%20Imphal%20airport%20is%20only%2070%20kms%20away%20Churachandpur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHangshing%20said%20the%20state%20government%20some%20time%20ago%20had%20issued%20an%20order%20asking%20all%20Kukis%20to%20return%20to%20their%20job%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20but%20not%20dealing%20with%20the%20question%20about%20their%20safety.%20On%20being%20told%20that%20BJP%20leader%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20CM%20Biren%2C%20R.K.%20Imo%20Singh%20recently%20urged%20all%20party%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20to%20attend%20the%20special%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20on%20August%2021%20stating%20that%20the%20administration%20would%20ensure%20their%20safety%2C%20he%20retorted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20only%20indicates%20that%20if%20the%20state%20administration%20wants%2C%20it%20can%20protect%20people%20which%20was%20not%20the%20case%20during%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20Kukis%20in%20valley%20districts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20have%20also%20noted%20that%20they%20are%20victims%20of%20%E2%80%9Csystematic%20ethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D%20and%20have%20appealed%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20sanction%20Rs%20500%20crore%20for%20%E2%80%9Cproper%20rehabilitation%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20security%20advisor%20for%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20Kuldiep%20Singh%2C%20had%20announced%20a%20relief%20package%20of%20Rs%20101.75%20crore%20for%20those%20displaced%20by%20the%20violence.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20disbursement%20has%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20groups%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20are%20scheduled%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20in%20New%20Delhi%20today.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20exclusively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fspecial-days-before-mha-was-to-finalise-kuki-accord-not-supported-by-cm-violence-broke-out-in-manipur%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20home%20ministry%20had%20been%20set%20to%20finalise%20a%20peace%20accord%20with%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20which%20CM%20Biren%20had%20not%20been%20in%20favour%20of%20%E2%80%93%20on%20May%208.%20Violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692248226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20162818%2Fimphal-long-shot-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-hill-kuki-zomi-mlas-dgp-chief-secretary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Besides%2C%20other%20key%20senior%20level%20posts%20in%20the%20civil%20and%20police%20department%20should%20also%20be%20created%20in%20public%20interest.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-hill-kuki-zomi-mlas-dgp-chief-secretary%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paramount%20Global%20Drops%20Plan%20to%20Sell%20Majority%20Stake%20in%20BET%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692248186000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2FParamount-Global-Logo.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235698565%22%2C%22summary%